title: Saint Louis Brass Quintet to open UALR’s Artspree series (University of Arkansas at Little Rock) ...
text: ( Source : University of Arkansas at Little Rock ) The University of Arkansas at Little Rock's first Artspree event of the 2015-16 season will feature one of America 's longest-standing brass quintets, Saint Louis Brass Quintet , at 7:30 p.m.
